o brother , where art thou ? is a 2001 american biographical drama film directed by joel coen and written by joel coen . the film stars george clooney , ethan coen , john turturro , and tim blake nelson . the film was directed by joel coen and written by joel coen . the film stars george clooney and ethan coen . the film was released in the united states on december 12 , 2001 . the film was released on december 12 , 2001 , by universal pictures .